{"tid":1550271,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果，真係如果，過唔到咁點","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:41:44.000Z","uid":76224,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f12d2ad7995ea7945d988b32352bf1f5901469eb","tid":1550271,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"唔係想潑冷水，只係見大家都咁樂觀，如果條《香港人權與民主法案》最後過唔到，希望大家唔會受唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a56febeb8e7a4096c5530becd60cb01d1de701","tid":1550271,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6d02ab82e3f5b5cc8c818763bd2844561504964","tid":1550271,"uid":127543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"到時咪靠自己囉，包生仔架咩，<br />\n贈你一句過時口號<br />\n自己香港自己救"},{"pid":"e5748534c4f66635c04e6a01c0c0bee8b411dc4c","tid":1550271,"uid":287755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"終極反送中英文年鑑上線了(整合9/6-4/9所有事件)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549878</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e58728dd316cc9044b6fa032af8188f59dc7b08b","tid":1550271,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"聽日唔玩激光唔玩火，一齊唱美國國歌感動美國國民！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars,<br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched,<br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare,<br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\nGave proof through the night,<br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\nOh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave."},{"pid":"bfb52cb438e34f0995c0848a25c6087d8dde6cbc","tid":1550271,"uid":259710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:24:05.000Z","msg":"呢條只係支線，仲要係optional嘅，主線都係靠自己啦，咁諗會好d，抗爭仲好漫長"},{"pid":"c4da37c8ff0d184a094e23a2b444e81d42a5309e","tid":1550271,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"到時再算啦"}]}